window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Washington, DC, has never been boring, but this is ridiculous. </p> <p>Warring witch covens. Werewolf packs fighting for territory. Rumors of human sacrifice. Minor problems leading up to Beltane, when the portents say the veils between worlds will shred. Did I mention the blood mage conspiracy using troll shock troops to take over the world? </p> <p>With a jaguar shifter, a handsome Nephilim, and a nest of feisty fairies watching my back, things should be fine. Right? </p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
